lias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/05\/20\/dhikr-solitude-remember-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24671,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Virtue of seclusion for remembrance of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThose in solitude have raced ahead.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, who are those in solitude?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThey are men and women who remember Allah often.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2676 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25140,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/08\/09\/wahb-head-health-is-diet\/","url_meta":{"origin":24671,"position":4},"title":"Wahb on Health: Foundation of health is diet, wisdom is silence","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 9, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibrahim ibn Muhammad reported: Wahb ibn Munabbih, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe doctors agreed that the head of medicine is diet. The wise men agreed that the head of wisdom is silence.\u201d Source: al-\u1e62amt li Ibn Ab\u012b Duny\u0101 619 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0625\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0641\u0650\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0628\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https: